name: The Abnuceals Emuukha Electric Orchestra
profile: There were two versions of the Abnuceals Emuukha Electric Symphony Orchestra, each playing [a=Frank Zappa]'s music.  The first version of the AEESO was an ensemble performing orchestration on [m=35641], conducted by [a362932].  The second was the 1975 [m=36013] incarnation, directed by [a470963], which also played two live concerts in Los Angeles.
